{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_11_01",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 1話 最終形態鬼モード",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "お～！　{user}さんじゃないですか～！\nこんな所でこころに会えるなんて幸運ですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh~! Isn’t that {user}-san~!\nWhat a lucky chance to meet Kokoro in a place like this~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.5746710103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "それとも、もしかしてBIG4になって大人気の\nこころを出待ちでもしてたんですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or maybe‚ were you waiting for Kokoro‚\nwho’s become super popular after becoming BIG4~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.0626757901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こんな所も何も俺達の仕事場だし\nなんなら俺はこころのマネージャーなんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "‘A place like this’? This is our workplace.\nBesides‚ I’m Kokoro’s manager…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "えー？　海外ツアー真っ最中で絶好調のアイドルに\nそんな態度とっていいんですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~? Is it okay to have such an attitude to an idol\nwho’s in the middle of a wildly successful overseas tour~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.9717483165
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "こころに会えるのは、アメリカから一時帰国してる\n今だけなんですよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can only see Kokoro right now‚ because\nshe’s temporarily back from America—!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4242769665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.4387098274
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく、異国の地での波乱万丈な日々を\nお話してあげようと思ったんですけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was about to tell you about\nmy eventful days abroad~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それは興味深いが今から企画書を作りに……\nうーん、まぁ少しならいいか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s interesting‚ but I have to make a project proposal now…\nHmm‚ well‚ a little is fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.9248335164
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "……それでですね、アメリカのファンからとーっても\n美味しいプリンの差し入れがあってですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ I got a super delicious pudding gift\nfrom my American fans~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.7666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（楽しんでくれたのは良かったが、いい加減仕事に）\n（戻らないとまずいな……こころには申し訳ないが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’m glad she’s enjoying it‚ but I really need to）\n（get back to work… I feel sorry for Kokoro though…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.9244204165
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "こころ！　本当にすまない！\nそろそろ仕事に戻らないといけなくてな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro! I’m really sorry!\nI need to get back to work soon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.1666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.1126491508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "む～……まぁお仕事なら仕方ないですね～\nまた今度、じーっくり続きを話してあげます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm~… Well‚ if it’s work‚ it can’t be helped~\nI’ll tell you the rest in detail next time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—That night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.776732886,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1233.3343505999892,
          "startTime": 84.0100672366
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1633.3333333000014,
          "startTime": 84.4100662193
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 83.9434005699
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 83.9434005699
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "ばーーーーんっ！！　お仕事終わりですね！\nさっきの続き、話してあげますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Baaam!! Work is over‚ right!\nI’ll tell you the rest from earlier~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.033333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "タイミングを見計らったかのように現れたな\n仕事もちょうど終わったし、ぜひ聞かせてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You appeared as if you were timing it perfectly.\nWork just finished too‚ so tell me all about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.533333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 99.2835698089
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり{user}さん、こころから\n海外珍道中の続きを聞きたくてたまらなかったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected‚ {user}-san‚ you actually\nwant to hear from Kokoro the rest of the overseas adventure‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 106.3411741537
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "では早速、アメリカでの莉央さんが\nどんな感じなのか、お話してあげましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ let me tell you\nhow Rio-san was in America.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.633333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "Grab the BIG4ではいろいろ\nありましたけど、ツアー中ずっと上機嫌なんですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A lot happened during \"Grab the BIG4\"‚\nbut she’s been in high spirits the whole tour~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 119.3591389301
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "休憩中にふわふわのパンケーキを振る舞ってくれたり\n朝ご飯も率先して作ってくれたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She even served fluffy pancakes during breaks‚\nand made breakfast proactively…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.2000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それだけじゃなくて積極的にみんなを\n誘って観光や外食に連れてってくれるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that’s not all. She makes sure\nto take everyone on sightseeing trips and meals out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.5666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.6870525322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、莉央さん……Grab the BIG4では\n思い詰めている様子だったから安心したよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ Rio-san… She seemed so worried during\n\"Grab the BIG4\"‚ so it’s a relief to hear her like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.5871886851
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "はい～。悩んでいた時とは違って本当に\n嬉しそうに笑ってくれて、こころも一安心ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes~. Unlike when she was troubled‚ she really\nsmiled happily‚ and Kokoro’s relieved too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.833333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.3480501773
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "でも……鬼の莉央さんも健在で～……\nうう、思い出すだけでも寒気が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… Demon Rio-san was still around…\nUgh‚ just remembering it gives me chills…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.533333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 158.0741955719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "何かやらかしたのか？　莉央さんが\nそこまで怒るなんてよほどのことだと思うんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did she do something wrong?\nRio-san getting that angry must mean it was serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.719656805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
